Current Status: High-confidence paradigms (tunneling, radical pairs, photosynthetic coherence) rest on convergent evidence. Others remain exploratory. Research prioritizes in vivo validation, interdisciplinary collaboration, and applications in medicine, sensing, and quantum tech. 

